msgstr "Onthoud: GIMP is vrije software.%n%nBezoek"

#: build/windows/installer/lang/setup.isl.xml.in:191
msgid "for free updates."
msgstr "voor gratis updates."

#: build/windows/installer/lang/setup.isl.xml.in:195
